# OUTPUT: 1 + 1 # -> 2
#         1 - 1 # -> 0
#         2 * 3 # -> 6
#         2 ** 4 # -> 16.0
#         6 / 2 # -> 3.0
#         2 // 3 # -> 0
#         7 % 3 # -> 1
#         -1 # -> -1
#         +1 # -> 1

# Unary
#    +       positive                         +1
#    &+      wrapping positive                &+1
#    -       negative                         -1
#    &-      wrapping negative                &-1
#    !       inversion                        !true
#    ~       binary complement                ~1
#
# Binary
#    &       binary AND                       1 & 2
#    |       binary OR                        1 | 2
#    ^       binary XOR                       1 ^ 2
#
# Shifts
#    <<      shift left, append               1 << 2
#    >>      shift right                      1 >> 2
#
# Equality
#    ==      equal                            1 == 2
#    !=      not equal                        1 != 2
#
# Inequalities
#    <       less                             1 < 2
#    <=      less or equal                    1 <= 2
#    >       greater                          1 > 2
#    >=      greater or equal                 1 >= 2
#    <=>     three-way comparison             1 <=> 2
#
# Addition
#    +       addition                         1 + 2
#    &+      wrapping addition                1 &+ 2
#
# Subtraction
#    -       subtraction                      1 - 2
#    &-      wrapping subtraction             1 &- 2
#
# Multiplication
#    *       multiplication                   1 * 2
#    &*      wrapping multiplication          1 &* 2
#
# Exponent
#    **      exponentiation                   1 ** 2
#    &**     wrapping exponentiation          1 &** 2
#
# Division
#    /       division                         1 / 2
#    //      floor division                   1 // 2
#
# Modulus (find the remainder of division)
#    %       modulus                          1 % 2
#
# Subsumption
#    ===     case subsumption                 "foo" === 5
#
# Logical
#    &&      logical AND                      true && false
#    ||      logical OR                       true || false
#
# Range
#    ..      inclusive range                  1..10
#    ...     exclusive range                  1...10
#
# Assignments
#    =       variable assignment              a = 1
#

1   e! 7 + 5 * 3
2   e! (3 + 4) * 2
3   

# OUTPUT: 7 + 5 * 3 # -> 22
#         3 + 4 * 2 # -> 14

# Unary                                 +, &+, -, &-, !, ~

#
# Binary OR/XOR                         |,^
#
# Equality and Subsumption              ==, !=, ===
#

# Logical OR                            ||
